to just walk by your parents?
- I think I'm ready.

00:14.348 --> 00:16.315
Let me see your face
as you walk by your parents.

00:18.318 --> 00:19.885
"why are you making
that face at us, riley?"

00:19.887 --> 00:22.354
Because I'm sneaking
onto the subway.

00:22.356 --> 00:23.822
- Out the window.
- Let's go.

00:27.527 --> 00:29.461
Daddy, what are you
doing here?

00:29.463 --> 00:32.598
