00:46.847 --> 00:49.348
Know how I know?
Look at ya.

00:49.350 --> 00:51.417
You're right here.

00:51.419 --> 00:55.220
How long do I have to live
in my father's world?

00:55.222 --> 00:57.289
Until you make it
yours.

00:57.291 --> 01:00.292
Riley, do you know what
I want more than anything?

01:00.294 --> 01:02.561
Go ahead,

01:02.563 --> 01:04.296
Make it yours.

01:04.298 --> 01:06.298
I will.
And when I do

01:06.300 --> 01:07.966
Will you still
be there for me?

01:07.968 --> 01:09.334
