who you are.

07:18.238 --> 07:20.639
Who are you?
I don't know who you are.

07:20.641 --> 07:22.808
Subway boy.

07:22.810 --> 07:25.377
I'm lucas friar
from austin, texas.

07:25.379 --> 07:27.212
Oh, new student,
mr. Friar?

07:27.214 --> 07:30.315
