- Great, you're just in time
for today's assignment.

07:30.317 --> 07:31.383
Have a seat.

07:32.385 --> 07:34.686
Okay, so we--

07:39.325 --> 07:42.127
So I'd like you guys
to open your books

07:42.129 --> 07:43.862
To page 48.

07:45.231 --> 07:47.265
Now I'd like you
to turn to page one.

07:48.334 --> 07:51.236
Now I'd like you to read
from page one to 48.

07:51.238 --> 07:54.706
