- It's not what I do anymore.

15:34.367 --> 15:37.168
- You're better than that.
- I'm just letting her be her.

15:46.645 --> 15:49.480
Ms. Hart,
you have detention.

15:49.482 --> 15:52.483
The principal will determine
if it goes further than that.

15:52.485 --> 15:54.218
Ms. Matthews,
please leave.

15:54.220 --> 15:57.155
- I deserve detention too.
- No, you don't.

15:57.157 --> 16:00.258
You didn't do anything.
And because you didn't
do anything,

16:00.260 --> 16:02.560
Your best friend
is in very deep trouble.

16:05.230 --> 16:06.731
All right, farkle,

16:06.733 --> 16:08.533
You can get down now.

16:08.535 --> 16:10.501
Well, you're actually
quite comfortable, sir.

16:10.503 --> 16:12.303
Thank you, farkle.

16:12.305 --> 16:13.438
Get off!

16:13.440 --> 16:15.506
Farkle isn't
going anywhere!

16:26.552 --> 16:28.653
Down, farkle.

16:31.623 --> 16:34.759
You're looking at us
pretty hard there,
mr. Matthews.

16:34.761 --> 16:36.561
I just want
to stand by my girl.

16:37.796 --> 16:39.564
You missed the moment
to stand by your girl.

16:39.566 --> 16:42.667
You were so busy trying
to be her, riley,

16:42.669 --> 16:45.636
You forgot
the best thing you can
do for her is be you.

16:46.839 --> 16:48.773
Riley, take farkle
for a walk.

16:54.913 --> 16:57.682
Listen, for as long
as I can remember,

16:57.684 --> 17:00.918
It's always been
riley and maya.

17:00.920 --> 17:04.822
Now I always believed
a friend helps another
friend out of trouble,

17:04.824 --> 17:05.890
Not into it.

17:07.826 --> 17:10.828
- I'm sorry.
- I am too.

17:10.830 --> 17:12.697
Because you go too far.

17:12.699 --> 17:14.866
Do you understand me?

17:16.902 --> 17:18.836
I have nobody at home

17:18.838 --> 17:20.972
Who helps me
with my homework.

17:35.921 --> 17:37.622
- Riles?
- Yeah?

17:37.624 --> 17:40.425
If we can't hang out
with each other as much
anymore,

17:40.427 --> 17:42.660
- Don't worry about it.
- Wait.

17:42.662 --> 17:44.929
- Why wouldn't we--
- he's going to make you
end the friendship.

17:44.931 --> 17:46.798
He said that?

17:46.800 --> 17:48.933
He's really upset
with me.

17:50.269 --> 17:52.003
He loves you.

17:52.005 --> 17:54.238
I don't think so
anymore.

17:54.240 --> 17:56.908
I just want you to know
that I get it wouldn't
be your fault.

17:56.910 --> 18:00.678
( laughs )
beyootiful!

18:00.680 --> 18:03.881
You two little bumblebees
got a sweet thing going.

18:03.883 --> 18:05.917
But where's your hunk?

18:07.019 --> 18:10.788
You ain't got no hunk,
you ain't got no story!

18:10.790 --> 18:13.724
- I haven't been
your good friend.
- You're my best friend.

18:13.726 --> 18:17.495
She's your best friend!
Best friends are important.

18:17.497 --> 18:20.765
I got a best friend.
I'm not talking to her
right now.

18:22.935 --> 18:25.736
I go too far.
And I don't think
that's gonna stop.

18:25.738 --> 18:29.507
- I'm bad for you.
- Did he say that?

18:29.509 --> 18:31.576
He will.

18:31.578 --> 18:33.311
This is your stop.

18:35.881 --> 18:37.648
Don't be me.

18:40.285 --> 18:43.654
- You don't go as far as me.
- No.

18:46.992 --> 18:48.626
- No.
- No!

18:48.628 --> 18:51.329
Do not push her
off this train!

18:51.331 --> 18:54.899
<i>You do not push</i>
<i>your best friend</i>
<i>off the train.</i>

18:57.636 --> 18:59.070
I'm not you.

19:04.843 --> 19:07.945
That little girl
pushed those doors open

19:07.947 --> 19:09.814
With the power of love.

19:09.816 --> 19:13.417
You are not allowed
to abandon our friendship!

19:13.419 --> 19:15.386
I would never do that.

19:15.388 --> 19:17.989
Riley, I'm pushing you away
because I'm not good
for you anymore.

19:17.991 --> 19:20.458
Only I decide that!

19:20.460 --> 19:22.693
- You know why?
- Why?

19:22.695 --> 19:25.530
Because if this is
my world now,

19:25.532 --> 19:28.399
The first person
I want in it is you.

19:29.601 --> 19:31.102
You're gonna save me,
aren't you?

19:32.604 --> 19:34.505
I am.

19:40.812 --> 19:42.680
Where is he?

19:44.850 --> 19:48.352
There is no way
I'm gonna let you break-up
my friendship with maya!

19:49.488 --> 19:51.355
Is that what you think
I want, riley?

19:52.491 --> 19:55.426
No.  What you said
you really want

19:55.428 --> 19:57.628
Is for me to make
the world my own.

19:57.630 --> 20:00.665
And you want me
to do my homework.

20:00.667 --> 20:02.700
Well, I'm doing it
right now.

20:04.603 --> 20:06.871
Here's what I think
is worth fighting for:

20:06.873 --> 20:09.807
This is my best friend.

20:09.809 --> 20:12.043
She's gonna get me
into trouble

20:12.045 --> 20:13.811
And I'm gonna
get us out of it.

20:15.614 --> 20:18.616
And I did.
Because here we are.

20:18.618 --> 20:22.553
Look at us, dad.
We're right here.

20:23.655 --> 20:26.958
My civil war
is over, dad.

20:26.960 --> 20:28.125
I won.

20:29.461 --> 20:31.095
What happens now?

20:39.871 --> 20:41.939
Friends, family--

20:41.941 --> 20:45.409
And all you other
subterranean mole people--

20:45.411 --> 20:47.612
We're here today
to celebrate

20:47.614 --> 20:49.747
Riley being riley.

20:51.016 --> 20:53.818
Now some may call this
a new york city subway pass.

20:53.820 --> 20:57.488
But you, riley,
can consider this
a ticket to the world.

20:57.490 --> 21:00.491
- You think I'm ready?
- You showed us you are.

21:00.493 --> 21:04.895
Riley, I've already
met the world.

21:04.897 --> 21:06.564
It's your turn.

21:08.967 --> 21:11.702
Hey, this isn't
so different from texas.

21:11.704 --> 21:14.772
- Look, there's a pony.
- That's a rat.

21:16.908 --> 21:18.809
- Ladies.
- Farkle.

21:23.949 --> 21:26.150
So where do
you wanna go?

21:26.152 --> 21:28.519
Don't know.
Big world.

21:28.521 --> 21:31.622
- Ours now?
- Yeah, but my dad did say

21:31.624 --> 21:32.690
I have to be home
by 5:00.

21:32.692 --> 21:35.760
Don't worry,
he wrote you a note.

21:40.032 --> 21:42.500
Conductor:
<i>Next stop, astor place,</i>

21:42.502 --> 21:44.068
<i>14th street...</i>

21:44.070 --> 21:45.770
<i>And the world.</i>

21:50.776 --> 21:52.710
You guys came back
and waited for us?

21:52.712 --> 21:55.479
Hey, we told you we were
always gonna be here for you.

21:55.481 --> 21:56.847
Yeah, riley.

21:56.849 --> 21:58.616
It's not so easy
handing over the world

21:58.618 --> 22:01.118
Without making sure
everything's going
to be okay.

22:05.724 --> 22:07.825
Well done,
mr. Matthews.

22:11.663 --> 22:14.031
<i>( theme music playing )</i>

22:15.067 --> 22:17.735
<i>♪ I'm singing "go-o-o."</i>
